---
const PODCAST_NAME = "[Podcast Name]";
const heroImg = "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1561758033-d89a9ad46330?w=1100&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop";
---
<section id="podcast" class="section section-soft scroll-mt-20 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="container-x">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-start">

      <!-- LEFT: cover-art tile + listen links -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-5">
        <div class="relative card-pillow overflow-hidden p-0"
             style="aspect-ratio: 1 / 1; background: linear-gradient(160deg, #2A1A0E 0%, #4A2F1A 50%, #D7261C 130%);">
          <img src={heroImg} alt=""
               class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover mix-blend-multiply opacity-50"/>
          <!-- concentric arcs -->
          <svg viewBox="0 0 400 400" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full opacity-20" aria-hidden="true">
            <g fill="none" stroke="#FFF7E8" stroke-width="1.4">
              <circle cx="80" cy="320" r="60"/>
              <circle cx="80" cy="320" r="120"/>
              <circle cx="80" cy="320" r="180"/>
              <circle cx="80" cy="320" r="260"/>
              <circle cx="80" cy="320" r="340"/>
            </g>
          </svg>
          <div class="relative h-full p-7 md:p-9 flex flex-col justify-end" style="color: var(--color-cream);">
            <span class="eyebrow eyebrow-light">A podcast from HiMFF</span>
            <p class="display-lg mt-2" style="color: var(--color-cream);">{PODCAST_NAME}</p>
            <p class="mt-4 max-w-[28ch] text-sm" style="color: rgba(255,247,232,0.85);">
              Long-form conversations with the people who run Hawai‘i’s food trucks.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary w-full justify-between mt-5">
          <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" class="h-4 w-4" aria-hidden="true" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <circle cx="10" cy="10" r="8"/><path d="M8 7l5 3-5 3z" fill="currentColor"/>
            </svg>
            Listen on the site
          </span>
          <span class="font-sans text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.16em] opacity-80">Coming soon</span>
        </a>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-2 mt-2">
          <a href="#" class="btn btn-ghost !py-2.5 text-xs justify-center">Na Leo TV</a>
          <a href="#" class="btn btn-ghost !py-2.5 text-xs justify-center">YouTube</a>
          <a href="#" class="btn btn-ghost !py-2.5 text-xs justify-center">Spotify</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- RIGHT: explainer -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-7">
        <span class="eyebrow">A closer look</span>
        <h2 class="h2-display" style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
          Why we record an hour and a half <span class="accent-script" style="color: var(--color-brand-red); font-size: 1.05em; line-height: 1;">when we only need fifteen.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="font-sans text-[18px] leading-[1.55] max-w-[42ch]" style="color: var(--color-ink-soft);">
          Every truck has a person behind the window — a reason they cook, a path that
          got them there, a thing they care about that you don’t hear in a five-minute
          order. The long-form is where that lives. The 15-minute Na Leo cut is the
          doorway in.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-10 grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-x-8 gap-y-7 max-w-[44ch]">
          <div>
            <p class="font-sans font-bold text-[12px] uppercase tracking-[0.08em] mb-2" style="color: var(--color-ink);">The long-form</p>
            <p class="font-sans text-[15px] leading-[1.6]" style="color: var(--color-ink-soft);">
              ~90-minute conversations, hosted here on the Foundation site (and YouTube).
              No edits for time, only for clarity.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-sans font-bold text-[12px] uppercase tracking-[0.08em] mb-2" style="color: var(--color-ink);">The TV cut</p>
            <p class="font-sans text-[15px] leading-[1.6]" style="color: var(--color-ink-soft);">
              A 15-minute version airs on <strong style="color: var(--color-ink);">Na Leo TV</strong>
              through their Community Creator Program — local public-access on Hawai‘i Island. The doorway in.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-sans font-bold text-[12px] uppercase tracking-[0.08em] mb-2" style="color: var(--color-ink);">Where we are</p>
            <p class="font-sans text-[15px] leading-[1.6]" style="color: var(--color-ink-soft);">
              Two episodes in the can, more on the calendar. Pre-launch — we publish
              here first.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-sans font-bold text-[12px] uppercase tracking-[0.08em] mb-2" style="color: var(--color-ink);">Want on the show?</p>
            <p class="font-sans text-[15px] leading-[1.6]" style="color: var(--color-ink-soft);">
              <a href="#vendors" class="font-medium">Tell us about your truck →</a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
